        <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted)">工具基於 PGSI（Problem Gambling Severity Index）量表。原作：Ferris, J., & Wynne, H. (2001). <em>The Canadian Problem Gambling Index: Final Report.</em> Canadian Centre on Substance Abuse. 量表為公開學術資源，本工具僅作教育用途。</p>
